## ✔ Security Auditing Basics

### Check Logged-in Users
```bash
who
w
```

### View Login History
```bash
last
```

### Lock User Account
```bash
sudo passwd -l intern1
```

### Force Password Change
```bash
sudo chage -d 0 dev1
```

